          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white m-0">SMS</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Universal reach, no app needed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
        Send and receive SMS via Twilio. Works with any phone number worldwide. Great for guests who don't use WhatsApp or for sending confirmation codes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-2">
        <a href="/docs/configuration/sms/" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Setup guide →</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 flex items-center justify-center">
